research/history/round_summaries/round_0171.json:54:      "If `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` is clearly worse than the two-stage mainline in both FVU and runtime metrics, close this parent branch for the current low-EF regime and return to `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round.",
