research/history/round_summaries/round_0094.json:53:      "Return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome; do not chain additional new-family probes."
research/history/round_summaries/round_0094.json:56:      "If `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` is clearly weaker than both the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor and the earlier soft-codebook probes, discard gated soft-codebook variants and resume mainline tuning next round.",
