research/history/logs/agent_round_0016.stdout.log:50:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 15 established `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=64` as a valid new Pareto point, so the next most informative single-variable question is whether LUTurbo can push cost lower again without collapsing reconstruction. This round changes only `K`, moving from `64` to `32` while keeping the same family and recipe fixed, to measure the next step on the cost-quality frontier.","summary":"Continue the topk low-K tradeoff lane: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `K` from `64` to `32` to test whether a materially cheaper decomposition still yields an acceptable reconstruction curve.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active topk family, changes exactly one primary variable, and follows directly from the new `K=64` keep result. The main risk is a sharp FVU jump at `K=32`, but mapping that boundary is now more valuable than more K128 recipe polishing because LUTurbo's objective is total online cost, not only anchor quality.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"32"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 15 added a credible `K=64` Pareto point on the accepted topk/signum/LR1.6e-3/EF12 backbone.","Round 16 continues the same low-K mapping by changing only `K` from 64 to 32.","Judge this run on frontier usefulness, not raw comparison to K128 alone: the key question is whether `K=32` remains deployably compatible with a tolerable quality drop for the lower online selection and summation cost."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=32` is still competitive enough, continue the same lane to `K=24` or `K=16` depending on curve shape and degradation size.","If `K=32` degrades sharply, `K=64` may be the practical low-K sweet spot for the current topk recipe.","If `K=32` is borderline but usable, compare it against `K=64` as a cost-quality tradeoff rather than against the K128 anchor alone."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0208.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"enter_low_cost_region_with_stronger_baseline","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 b_i 来自单个静态向量库；导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单样本 top-k 选择后的单库查表与加权求和，因此属于直接兼容。r207 表明在相同 K=64、EF=2 下，topk 的 FVU 明显优于 factorized_topk，说明 <0.5x 区域的主要瓶颈很可能来自 scorer factorization 而非纯预算。本轮保持 architecture=topk、K=64、optimizer、LR 不变，只把 EXPANSION_FACTOR 从 2 降到 1，直接压低 encoder selection cost，目标是在进入 <0.5x 区域的同时，测试非 factorized 单库 baseline 能否拿到明显优于 factorized_topk@0.44x 的 FVU。按成本表线性外推，selection cost 约可从 0.50x 降到 0.25x，total_cost 约落在 0.31x。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K64 的 FVU 仍明显优于 factorized_topk 在相近成本下的结果，则下一步可固定 EF=1，单变量扫描 K=96 或 K=128，寻找 <0.5x 内更好的 topk 前沿点。","如果 EF=1 导致 FVU 大幅恶化，则说明 topk 的有效区间仍依赖更大的字典规模，下一步应回到 EF=2 并尝试其他低成本 family，而不是继续压缩 topk 字典。"],"notes_to_memory":["r207 已证明在 K=64、EF=2 下，去掉 factorized scorer 能显著改善 FVU，因此值得沿 topk 继续走 encoder 降本轴。","本轮只改 EXPANSION_FACTOR，保持 K 不变，便于把性能变化归因为字典规模而不是 lookup 次数变化。"],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor","self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则，并直接服务于当前 <0.5x 区域补点目标。主要风险是 EF=1 可能使 topk 表达能力下降较多，但其信息价值高，因为它能直接回答非 factorized 简单架构能否在真正低成本区站住脚。","summary":"在直接兼容的 topk family 上做单变量低成本下探：固定 K=64、signum、LR=3e-3，仅把 EXPANSION_FACTOR 从 2 降到 1，目标是在约 0.31x 总成本处建立一个比 factorized_topk 更强的 <0.5x 候选点。","touched_files":[]}
