research/history/logs/agent_round_0089.stdout.log:58:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual`, `lowrank_residual_vq`, `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`, `lowrank_gated_residual`, and `lowrank_grouped_residual` all failed to challenge the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the most informative remaining matched architecture probe is the plain `lowrank_residual` family. It preserves the same low-rank trunk and static-library weighted-sum export path while removing the extra second residual stage and auxiliary selector structure, making it the cleanest test of whether the current mainline's quality advantage truly requires two-stage residual allocation. If `lowrank_residual` is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then the simpler single-stage low-rank family is not worth continuing in the current LUTurbo-aligned regime.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` to `lowrank_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the matched architecture probe rule by changing only `architecture` and keeping the mainline `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe fixed. `lowrank_residual` is the strongest remaining LUTurbo-aligned probe because it is the simplest low-rank static-library decomposition still comparable to the current mainline, and it directly tests whether the second residual pass is buying necessary quality or only extra online cost. The main risk is that the family may underfit badly at matched K128, but that negative result would still answer the exact worth-continuing question cleanly.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 89 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_residual` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Judge this run strictly as a family-worthiness test for the simplest low-rank single-stage residual decomposition; the core question is whether dropping the second residual stage can preserve enough quality to justify the lower expected online cost.","Return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome; do not chain another new-family probe immediately after this one."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, discard it and resume mainline tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round.","If `lowrank_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a viable lower-cost branch but still return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round per probe policy."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0194.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，residual 分支 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和。factorized scorer 只改变在线选择打分路径，不改变最终 decoder 形式，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，lowrank_factorized_residual 是否能以更低 encoder selection cost（约 0.5x h×n）提供一个仍值得保留的低成本支线；若 FVU 明显劣于 lowrank_residual，则说明 factorized scorer 在当前低 EF regime 下损失过大，不值得继续作为主线兼容方向。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_factorized_residual 明显劣于 lowrank_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若它在显著更低 selection_cost 下维持可接受 FVU 且训练更快，可将 factorized scorer 保留为低成本 selector 方向。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出路径仍是 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态字典库的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","r193 已确认 plain lowrank_residual 在 0.62x selection cost 下 FVU=0.0730；本轮进一步隔离 factorized scorer 是否值得用额外误差换更低选择成本。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，科学问题单一明确：验证 factorized scorer 这类低成本选择机制在兼容 residual family 中是否值得继续。虽然其现有 frontier 点较弱，但它能直接回答‘更便宜的 selector 是否还能保住可用 FVU’这一部署相关问题，信息价值高于重复已失败的 soft-codebook siblings。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 lowrank_factorized_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构仍是 trunk 静态库与 residual 静态字典上的有限加权和，属扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即 factorized scorer 带来的更低 encoder 成本是否足以让该 family 继续作为 LUTurbo 低成本候选。","touched_files":[]}
