age_soft_codebook_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: export path is identical to the mainline soft-codebook two-stage family; only stage budget allocation changes.","This is the cleanest remaining matched architecture probe because it preserves the mainline's static libraries and likely feasible encoder cost, avoiding another likely policy-reject like routed/bucketed variants.","When reviewing the run, check not just FVU but also `tokens_per_sec`, total runtime, and `final_total_tokens` to see whether any gain is offset by slower training."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes, while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` stay fixed. I am avoiding another clearly over-budget probe and choosing a matched variant that isolates one architectural question while remaining compatible with LUTurbo export and likely feasible under the selection-cost constraint.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` as the one matched architecture change against the current mainline recipe. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`), keeps the same static trunk/codebook/residual libraries, and tests whether a front-loaded two-stage residual budget is worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime.","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0202.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"matched_probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，soft codebook 项 Σ_m pi_m c_m 可导出为静态 codebook 库上的加权和，residual 项 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路。兼容性判断为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 是否已经足够接近当前 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线，从而说明第二个 residual refinement stage 在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下边际价值不足，不值得继续承担额外 encoder 选择成本与潜在训练时延。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 在 FVU 上接近当前主线且 tokens_per_sec 更高或总耗时更低，则记录为更优低成本/低时延备选，但下一轮仍按策略回到 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线。","若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 明显落后于当前主线，则说明第二阶段 residual refinement 在 EF=2 下仍有明确结构价值，后续应继续围绕主线做成本轴微调而不是退回单阶段。","若该 probe 运行明显更慢但 FVU 改善不足，则把单阶段 soft-codebook 也视为负面信号，不继续展开该 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 的 LUTurbo 导出形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + codebook 静态库 + residual 静态字典的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","该 family 在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 明显低于当前 two-stage 主线，因此它是检验第二阶段 refinement 是否值得的最直接低成本对照。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更高训练代价误判为架构优势。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这次严格沿用历史已通过的 architecture action 形状：architecture 只由 family_name 指定，不在 env_overrides 中重复声明，从而避免前两轮的 policy_reject。科学问题也保持单一明确，只测试 two-stage 主线中的第二 residual stage 是否在 EF=2 的兼容成本区间内值得保留。","summary":"执行一个合法的 matched architecture probe：family_name 切到 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该 family 的最终重构仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态查表链路，兼容性为扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即当前主线中的第二个 residual refinement stage 是否真的值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
