research/history/logs/agent_action_0099.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 98 was the first signum LR probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` to beat the archived `LR=2.0e-3` K128 baseline, so before opening the optimizer branch the next single question should be whether `LR=2.4e-3` is a reproducible new anchor rather than a one-off improvement. Re-running the exact same `2.4e-3` recipe is the cleanest way to judge whether the full curve remains stronger than the `2.0e-3` and `1.6e-3` runs, especially in early/mid descent and late stability, rather than trusting the endpoint alone.","summary":"Stay on the `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline and run a clean confirmation of the promising higher-LR recipe with `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=2.4e-3`, changing no other recipe variable.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"confirm_baseline","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays within the same family, keeps `K` and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and changes no new axis beyond confirming the only signum LR setting that has actually improved the endpoint so far. The tradeoff is spending one round on confirmation instead of opening the optimizer branch immediately, but that is justified because the mainline anchor should be localized on a reproducible LR before optimizer comparisons are made.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.4e-3"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 99 is a clean confirmation run for the first improved signum LR candidate on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`: `LR=2.4e-3` at `K=128`, `EF=12`, and `OPTIMIZER=signum`.","Judge this round by curve-shape repeatability against the archived `LR=2.0e-3`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and Round 98 `LR=2.4e-3` runs, not by endpoint alone.","Only after confirming whether `LR=2.4e-3` is a stable anchor should the optimizer branch open on this family."],"next_hypotheses":["If `LR=2.4e-3` reproduces the stronger curve or endpoint, promote it to the operative signum mainline LR and test `OPTIMIZER=adam` next at that settled recipe.","If the `LR=2.4e-3` repeat falls back to a near-tie or worse than `LR=2.0e-3`, close the signum LR branch with `LR=2.0e-3` as the operative anchor and test `OPTIMIZER=adam` next there.","Do not change loss, preprocess, or `K` until the optimizer question has been isolated from the settled signum baseline."],"primary_variable":"baseline_confirmation"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0118.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.015625"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。当前 EF=2 已稳定满足 encoder 选择成本硬约束，`signum + LR=3.0e-3` 是已复现的低成本主线锚点，而 `adam` 在同配方下直接爆炸，说明 optimizer 分支可暂时关闭。按主线顺序，下一步应进入 loss/preprocess 轴；本轮只改一个主变量 `AUXK_ALPHA`，将其从默认 `0.03125` 下调到 `0.015625`，回答唯一问题：在低 EF 可部署 regime 下，较弱的辅助稀疏正则是否能减少对主重构目标的干扰，从而改善 FVU，同时几乎不增加训练运行代价。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果较低 `AUXK_ALPHA` 改善终点或曲线形状，且 `tokens_per_sec`、总耗时、`final_total_tokens` 基本不变，则再做一次 clean baseline 复现确认。","如果较低 `AUXK_ALPHA` 无益或退化，则关闭该 loss 分支，保留默认 `0.03125` 并再考虑其他轻量 loss/preprocess 轴。","在 loss/preprocess 轴未得出清晰信号前，不改 K，也不改 TRUNK_RANK / NUM_CODES / STAGE1_RATIO / FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式不变，仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","Optimizer 分支结论：`adam` 在 EF=2、LR=3.0e-3 下出现爆炸性退化，应回到 `signum + LR=3.0e-3` 主线锚点。","本轮严格单变量，只改 `AUXK_ALPHA`；这是 loss 轴上的轻量改动，不会改变 encoder 选择成本，也不应显著增加训练时长。重点继续检查曲线形状、`tokens_per_sec`、总耗时与 `final_total_tokens`。"],"primary_variable":"auxk_alpha","self_review":"这符合当前主线顺序：EF 已确认在预算内，clean baseline 与 LR 轴已完成，optimizer 分支也因 `adam` 爆炸而得到负结论，因此现在应转向 loss/preprocess。选择 `AUXK_ALPHA` 而不是更重的 preprocess 变化，是因为它改动最小、归因最清晰、运行代价最低。","summary":"关闭 `adam` 分支，回到已复现的 `signum + LR=3.0e-3` 主线配方，仅将 `AUXK_ALPHA` 从 `0.03125` 下调到 `0.015625`，测试更弱辅助稀疏正则能否在低成本 EF=2 regime 下进一步改善 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0139.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"STAGE1_RATIO","value":"0.75"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束；本轮只改两阶段预算分配，不改变 family、EF、K、optimizer、LR，也不改变最终导出形式。r138 表明把 LR 下调到 2.4e-3 会在相同吞吐和相同总 token 下把整条曲线都拉差，说明“LR 偏大”假设已基本排除；而 `adam` 在该可行主线上已有明确负信号，AUXK/TRUNK_RANK/NUM_CODES 近几轮也未给出新增益。当前尚未被回答的单一问题是：在相同总 K=128 下，将两阶段预算从默认近似 50/50 改为更前置的 STAGE1_RATIO=0.75，是否能让第一阶段承担更多粗重构，从而改善低 EF regime 的中后段收敛并把 FVU 压回 0.0581 以下。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 STAGE1_RATIO=0.75 改善终点 FVU 或曲线中后段形状，则继续在同 family 上围绕 stage budget 做更细的单变量搜索。","若 STAGE1_RATIO=0.75 明显变差，则说明低 EF 主线不受益于前置预算，后续可反向测试更保守的 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 或关闭该轴。","若 STAGE1_RATIO=0.75 与 baseline 几乎等价，则说明两阶段预算分配不是当前瓶颈，后续应回到更贴近 deploy 成本的已知轴而非继续做 recipe 微调。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的导出形式未变，仍属扩展兼容，可继续作为 LUTurbo 主线 family。","r138 在相同 tokens_per_sec 与 final_total_tokens 下整条曲线变差，基本排除了“把 signum LR 从 3.0e-3 下调到 2.4e-3 会改善收敛”的假设。","在 optimizer 与常见 loss 轴都缺乏正信号后，STAGE1_RATIO 是当前仍未回答、且不改变导出契约的两阶段内部预算问题。"],"primary_variable":"stage1_ratio","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 STAGE1_RATIO，family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 保持当前主线参考配方不变。该动作保持 LUTurbo 导出契约不变，且不应触碰 encoder 选择成本硬约束；风险是 75/25 过于激进，可能重演历史上非对称预算的负信号，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构；在 clean baseline 与 LR 下降试验之后，转向尚未回答的两阶段内部预算问题：保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变，只把 STAGE1_RATIO 设为 0.75，测试更前置的 stage1 预算能否在不增加在线成本的前提下改善低 EF 主线的收敛与 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0016.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 15 established `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=64` as a valid new Pareto point, so the next most informative single-variable question is whether LUTurbo can push cost lower again without collapsing reconstruction. This round changes only `K`, moving from `64` to `32` while keeping the same family and recipe fixed, to measure the next step on the cost-quality frontier.","summary":"Continue the topk low-K tradeoff lane: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `K` from `64` to `32` to test whether a materially cheaper decomposition still yields an acceptable reconstruction curve.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active topk family, changes exactly one primary variable, and follows directly from the new `K=64` keep result. The main risk is a sharp FVU jump at `K=32`, but mapping that boundary is now more valuable than more K128 recipe polishing because LUTurbo's objective is total online cost, not only anchor quality.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"32"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 15 added a credible `K=64` Pareto point on the accepted topk/signum/LR1.6e-3/EF12 backbone.","Round 16 continues the same low-K mapping by changing only `K` from 64 to 32.","Judge this run on frontier usefulness, not raw comparison to K128 alone: the key question is whether `K=32` remains deployably compatible with a tolerable quality drop for the lower online selection and summation cost."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=32` is still competitive enough, continue the same lane to `K=24` or `K=16` depending on curve shape and degradation size.","If `K=32` degrades sharply, `K=64` may be the practical low-K sweet spot for the current topk recipe.","If `K=32` is borderline but usable, compare it against `K=64` as a cost-quality tradeoff rather than against the K128 anchor alone."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0131.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态向量库，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮只回答一个问题：在 clean baseline 已稳定复现且 signum 连续多轮无改进后，改用 adam 并将 LR 联动下调到 1.0e-3，是否能带来更平滑的训练曲线和更低的最终 FVU，同时不显著恶化 tokens_per_sec 与总耗时。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 adam@1.0e-3 曲线更稳且终点更好，可继续在同 family/EF=2/K=128 上细调 LR（如 7.0e-4 或 1.3e-3）。","若 adam@1.0e-3 终点接近但明显更慢，应把它视为负面信号并回到 signum 主线。","若 adam@1.0e-3 明显欠收敛或发散，则结束 optimizer 分支，下一轮再考虑 loss/preprocess 而非继续扫 optimizer。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容；本轮不是结构改动，只是 optimizer 轴探索。","EF=2 继续保证 selection_cost 在预算内；K 保持 128，不把部署查表成本变化与 optimizer 效应混杂。","r130 clean baseline 已复现当前 feasible frontier，因此可把后续变化更可靠地归因到 optimizer/LR 联动。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"遵守主线推进与单变量原则：family、EF、K 均固定，只切换 optimizer，并按历史规则联动重调 LR 以避免无效比较。风险是 adam 可能带来更慢吞吐或更长收敛时间，因此必须同时检查曲线形状、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens。","summary":"在已稳定复现的 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线上测试一次 optimizer 变化：固定 EF=2、K=128，仅把优化器从 signum 切到 adam，并把 LR 配套下调到 1.0e-3，判断是否存在比当前 feasible baseline 更好的收敛形状与 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0114.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都对应静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。Round 112 与 Round 113 已在 EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=2.4e-3 下复现同一可行 Pareto 点，说明成本预算内的 clean baseline 已确认；本轮只改一个主变量 `LR`，上探到 3.0e-3，回答唯一问题：在 EF=2 的低成本 regime 下，略高一步长能否在不牺牲稳定性和吞吐的前提下改善全程下降形状或终点 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LR=3.0e-3` 改善终点或明显加快早中期下降且运行代价未恶化，则将其作为新的 signum 主线学习率候选并考虑一次复现确认。","如果 `LR=3.0e-3` 出现震荡、退化或吞吐/总时长明显变差，则关闭向上 LR 分支，保留 `LR=2.4e-3` 作为 EF=2 主线锚点。","在 LR 轴结论明确前，不切换 optimizer、不改 K，也不改其他成本相关结构参数。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","EF=2 已在 Round 112 和 Round 113 下稳定落在选择成本预算内，当前 frontier 可行点为 cost≈1.25x、FVU≈0.05914。","本轮遵守单变量原则，只改 `lr`；重点同时观察曲线形状、`tokens_per_sec`、总耗时与 `final_total_tokens`，避免为微小 FVU 改善付出过高运行代价。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"这符合当前主线顺序：EF 已确认可行，clean baseline 已补齐，下一步应只做学习率局部化。选择向上探测而不是改 optimizer，是因为现有 EF=2 曲线已稳定但仍有继续下降迹象，最值得先测试的是更积极一步长是否能带来更好的收敛效率；同时没有引入第二个变量，归因清晰。","summary":"在已确认成本可行且可复现的 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` EF=2 主线上，仅将 `LR` 从 `2.4e-3` 上调到 `3.0e-3`，测试更高 signum 步长能否改善低成本 regime 的收敛曲线和终点 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
