research/history/logs/agent_action_0113.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.4e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都可静态导出为固定向量库上的有限加权和，因此可落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。Round 112 已证明 EF=2 时该主线 family 进入选择成本预算内（约 1.25x h×n）并得到 FVU=0.05914，但这只是首个成本可行点。按当前主线顺序，下一轮应先补 clean baseline：完全复现 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=2.4e-3`，确认该低成本 Pareto 点是否可重复、曲线是否仍保持从 0.0966 -> 0.0655 -> 0.0591 的健康下降，而不是立即再动 LR 或其他配方轴。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 EF=2 clean baseline 复现出接近 0.059 的终点且曲线仍健康，再只改 `lr` 做单变量微调。","如果 clean baseline 明显回退或曲线形状不稳，则先把该点降级为不稳定候选，不急于开 optimizer 分支。","如果复现时仍显示 late-stage 继续改善且吞吐/总耗时稳定，再考虑是否需要更长训练而不是立刻改结构。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","Round 112 的 EF=2 可行点已满足成本预算，并且 `curve_still_improving=true`、`tokens_per_sec≈166553`、`final_total_tokens≈59.97M`，说明当前更需要确认可重复性而不是同时打开新配方轴。","本轮严格单变量原则下不再改变 EF/LR/optimizer/K；问题只是在低成本主线 recipe 上补一次 clean baseline。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"这符合当前策略顺序：先确认 EF 在预算内，再补 clean baseline。虽然 env_overrides 与 Round 112 相同，但这正是本轮要隔离的唯一问题，即该 EF=2 主线点是否稳定可复现。没有同时引入 LR、optimizer、K 或结构变化，归因最干净。","summary":"在当前成本可行主线 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 上补一次 clean baseline，完整复现 `EF=2, K=128, signum, LR=2.4e-3`，先确认这个 LUTurbo 可部署 Pareto 点的稳定性与曲线形状，再决定是否进入 LR 微调。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0071.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 70 answered the first `two_stage_residual` LR probe negatively: lowering `LR` from `2.0e-3` to `1.6e-3` produced a uniformly worse curve, with weaker start, weaker mid-course descent, and a worse endpoint than the archived baseline. The next single mainline question, still within the prescribed LR-before-optimizer order, is whether a modest upward shift improves early and mid-course descent without destabilizing training: does raising `LR` to `2.4e-3` beat or at least match the archived `2.0e-3` `two_stage_residual` baseline on full-curve shape?","summary":"Stay on the `two_stage_residual` mainline and revert to the archived baseline recipe, changing only `LR` from `2.0e-3` to `2.4e-3` while keeping `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and the baseline aux/runtime settings fixed. Judge this run by the whole trajectory against the archived `2.0e-3` baseline, especially whether the higher step size improves descent without introducing instability or a worse finish.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This remains on the active mainline family, respects the fixed `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` rule, uses an allowed `K`, and changes exactly one primary variable: `lr`. It follows the required sequence because the clean baseline is already established and Round 70 showed that lower LR is not the right direction; the highest-value next question is the symmetric upward LR probe before opening the optimizer branch. The main risk is overshooting and adding instability, but that is precisely what this single-variable test is designed to resolve.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.4e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 70 established that `two_stage_residual` with `LR=1.6e-3` is uniformly worse than the archived `2.0e-3` baseline across start, mid, and end of the curve, so the lower-LR branch should not be favored.","Round 71 is the complementary within-family LR probe: test `LR=2.4e-3` against the archived `two_stage_residual` baseline at `K=128`, `EF=12`, and `signum`, and judge it by full-curve shape rather than endpoint alone."],"next_hypotheses":["If `LR=2.4e-3` improves endpoint or gives a clearly stronger overall curve than `2.0e-3`, archive it as the new `two_stage_residual` mainline recipe.","If `LR=2.4e-3` is noisier or clearly worse, keep `2.0e-3` as the settled signum LR and move to the optimizer question next.","If `LR=2.4e-3` is mixed, do at most one final LR-localization round before changing optimizer."],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0217.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"240"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214-r216 已经连续证明在 EF=1 下沿 K 轴增加查表预算能稳定压低 <0.5x 区域的 FVU，而 r216 仍从 0.1635 改善到 0.1528，说明边际收益尚未耗尽；因此本轮继续在同一最短链路 family 上仅把 K 提到 240，目标是在总成本仍预计约 0.49x、继续留在 <0.5x 区域的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 再向下压一截，并判断 topk@EF1 的收益是否开始真正接近平台。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K240 继续明显改善 FVU 且运行代价未恶化，则低开销区仍可再补一个贴边点。","如果 K240 的收益很小或训练时间明显变差，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 已接近边际收益极限，后续应转向新的低成本 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 目前是 <0.5x 区域最稳的直接兼容主线，且导出路径最简单，适合继续补低开销 Pareto 前沿。","r214-r216 已形成清晰趋势：在 EF=1 固定 encoder 成本下，增加 K 可以持续降低 FVU，因此当前最高信息量的单变量仍是 K 轴。","评估时必须同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认贴近 0.5x 边界后的额外查表预算是否仍值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮选择 K=240 而不是直接上到 256，是为了尽量稳妥地继续留在 <0.5x 区域，同时测试靠近边界时的真实边际收益。风险是收益可能已开始明显变小，但这正是当前需要量化的关键信号。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 240，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1528 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0066.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 65 established `two_stage_residual` as the new mainline by materially beating the previous `gated` K128 control under the matched `signum`/`2.0e-3` recipe, so the highest-value next step is to convert that one-off probe into a clean mainline baseline before touching learning rate or optimizer. This round answers one question only: does the same `two_stage_residual` K128 EF12 `signum` `2.0e-3` recipe reproduce a similarly strong curve as a stable baseline worth tuning from, or was Round 65 an overoptimistic single run.","summary":"Run a clean baseline repeat for the new `two_stage_residual` mainline at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=2.0e-3`, changing no recipe variable beyond promoting the family into baseline confirmation.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"confirm_baseline","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"baseline","self_review":"This follows the mainline progression rule by staying within the same family and using the recommended next step of establishing a clean baseline before any LR or optimizer change. The round changes no substantive training variable, so the result will be easy to attribute and will tell us whether the promising staged-residual curve is robust enough to tune further.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 66 promotes `two_stage_residual` from matched probe winner to mainline candidate by running a clean baseline repeat before any recipe tuning.","Judge this round primarily by reproducibility of the training curve shape and final FVU relative to Round 65, not just by whether the endpoint is slightly above or below 0.1278.","If the baseline reproduces cleanly, the next mainline question should be a single learning-rate adjustment inside `two_stage_residual`; if it fails to reproduce, investigate stability before changing optimizer or K."],"next_hypotheses":["If the clean baseline reproduces the strong Round 65 curve, test one learning-rate adjustment within `two_stage_residual` next.","If the clean baseline is materially worse or less stable, rerun only if needed to separate variance from recipe instability before changing optimizer.","If the curve is strong early but plateaus oddly, use the next round for a single LR change rather than touching K or architecture."],"primary_variable":"baseline_confirmation"}
