research/history/logs/agent_action_0154.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r153 已用 clean baseline 重新确认主线参考配方在当前运行环境下能稳定回到 FVU≈0.058106 且总耗时降回 294s，说明近期慢速样本更像吞吐波动而非 family 退化；因此本轮只回答一个问题：在主线 family、K、EF、optimizer 与导出形式不变的前提下，把 LR 从 3.0e-3 上调到此前两次出现更低终点的 3.3e-3，能否在正常吞吐区间内稳定复现更好的中后段收敛与更低 FVU，而不是仅仅依赖异常慢速运行。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 3.3e-3 在接近 r153 的 tokens_per_sec/总耗时下再次稳定优于 3.0e-3，则把 3.3e-3 升格为该 family 的 signum 主线 LR。","若 3.3e-3 回落到接近 3.0e-3，或只有在明显更慢时才略优，则关闭 LR 上调分支，保留 3.0e-3 作为更稳的主线锚点。","若 3.3e-3 终点更好但曲线出现更早震荡或平台，则不再继续上探 LR，后续只在已确认较优的 LR 上考虑 optimizer 或更贴近系统成本的单变量轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 继续满足选择成本预算；K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与 LR 轴混杂。","r153 clean baseline 恢复到 294s，说明近期 391s/453s 更可能是吞吐异常而非训练更长。","评估本轮时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，判断 3.3e-3 的收益是否独立于运行时慢速样本。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 全部固定在当前主线参考配方。按照推荐顺序，EF 已确认在预算内，clean baseline 已补齐，现在进入学习率轴是最小且可归因的下一步。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；在 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 固定的前提下，仅把 LR 从 3.0e-3 调到 3.3e-3，验证此前的小幅 FVU 改善能否在正常运行代价下稳定复现。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0215.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"192"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214 已证明在 EF=1 下把 K 从 64 提到 128 能把 <0.5x 区域的 FVU 从 0.2583 压到 0.1968，说明当前低开销区的主瓶颈更像是查表预算不足，而不是 topk family 已经到头；因此本轮继续沿同一最短链路 family 提升 K 到 192，目标是在总成本仍预计约 0.43x、明显低于 0.5x 的条件下，进一步压低低开销区最佳 FVU，验证 topk@EF1 是否还能继续向可用前沿逼近。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K192 在 <0.5x 内继续明显改善 FVU 且吞吐下降可接受，则同 family 的低开销前沿可继续沿 K 轴补一个更细点。","如果 K192 的收益很小但训练时间或 tokens_per_sec 明显变差，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 的边际收益开始耗尽，后续应转向新的低成本 family 而不是再加查表预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 是当前唯一已在 <0.5x 区域稳定形成两个可行点的直接兼容 family，且导出路径最简单，适合作为低开销主线基准。","r214 已经给出明确正信号：在 EF=1 保持 encoder 成本不变时，增加 K 能显著改善 FVU，因此当前最有信息量的单变量仍是 K 轴。","评估时必须同步检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认新增查表预算是否值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮延续已验证有效的低开销 topk 主线，不再重复被 policy 卡住的 lowrank_factorized_residual param_only 路线。选择 K=192 而不是先补 K=96，是因为当前任务优先级是尽快把 <0.5x 区域的最佳 FVU 压低，而不是细化已明显被 K=128 支配的中间点；风险是更高 K 可能带来吞吐下降和更长总耗时。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 192，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1968 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0030.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"A clean rerun of the matched `gated` baseline at `K=128, EF=12, optimizer=signum, lr=1.6e-3` will tell us whether Round 29 was a stable result with a healthy curve shape or a one-off; if it reproduces near 0.1499 with smooth descent, we should keep `gated` on the mainline and start the LR sweep next.","summary":"Round 29 already established the first matched `gated` control and it slightly leads the current frontier at `K=128`, so the highest-value next step is not to branch or change K, but to pay the clean-baseline tax the strategy asks for. This answers one question only: whether `gated` is genuinely competitive under the reference recipe, judged by both final FVU and the training-curve shape.","change_type":"no_change","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the required family, keeps EF fixed at 12, does not touch K, and follows the requested sequencing by filling the clean baseline before LR or optimizer changes. I am intentionally not proposing a new LR yet because reproducibility and curve shape are the blocking question after a first promising gated run.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 30 should be a clean control rerun for gated at the matched reference recipe: K=128, EF=12, signum, LR=1.6e-3.","Use the rerun to inspect trajectory shape, not just terminal FVU; only start the LR sweep if the baseline reproduces cleanly."],"next_hypotheses":["If the clean rerun reproduces with a smooth curve, try a conservative LR callback within gated, starting with 1.2e-3.","If the clean rerun is clearly worse or unstable versus Round 29, archive gated quickly and return to the topk mainline."],"primary_variable":"other_param"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0153.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r150-r152 的 matched architecture probes 已经依次表明去掉 second stage、去掉 soft-codebook、退回 topk 都会明显恶化 FVU，因此当前问题不再是 family 本身值不值得继续，而是回到主线后重新建立一个干净的运行时与曲线锚点：在保持主线参考配方 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / K=128 / EF=2 / signum / LR=3.0e-3 不变的前提下，确认其 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens 是否仍稳定可复现，从而为后续单变量 recipe 决策提供可信基线。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 复现 0.0581 左右的终点且吞吐恢复到正常区间，则下一轮再进入单变量学习率或优化器判断。","若 clean baseline 仍出现明显慢速但终点稳定，则把近期问题归因为运行时吞吐波动而非架构退化，后续 recipe 评估必须继续把总耗时与 tokens_per_sec 作为硬约束。","若 clean baseline 自身终点或曲线形状发生漂移，则先停止扩展 recipe 搜索，优先确认主线锚点后再做下一步单变量扰动。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 已满足选择成本预算，K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与主线复验混杂。","r150-r152 的架构探针已经说明主线 family 相对近邻与简单 baseline 都有真实结构收益，本轮按规则回到主线。","评估本轮时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，区分是训练更长还是吞吐更慢导致耗时上升。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"本轮不新开 family，回到主线参考配方做 clean baseline 复验，符合当前主线推进顺序。虽然这一步不直接追求更低 FVU，但在近期多轮 probe 与明显运行时波动后，先恢复可信锚点比继续做难归因的 recipe 扰动更稳妥。","summary":"回到主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，固定 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3，不引入任何新结构或 recipe 变化，先做一轮干净 baseline 复验，确认当前主线的真实训练曲线与运行代价。","touched_files":[]}
