research/history/logs/agent_action_0031.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Within the `gated` mainline at `K=128, EF=12, optimizer=signum`, a conservative LR step down from `1.6e-3` to `1.2e-3` may improve stability and early-to-mid training curve smoothness enough to beat the current `0.149866` result; this round asks only whether the matched `gated` recipe is slightly overdriven at the reference LR.","summary":"Round 30's clean-baseline proposal was rejected by policy, so the next valid mainline move is the first LR callback while holding family, K, EF, and optimizer fixed. This stays on `gated`, changes only LR, and is explicitly aimed at reading the curve shape: if `1.2e-3` descends more smoothly and avoids late flattening or noise while matching or improving terminal FVU, keep sweeping LR inside `gated`; if it is simply slower and worse throughout, the reference LR remains the right anchor.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"small","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This obeys the one-variable rule by changing only LR, keeps EF at 12 and K at 128, and follows the prescribed mainline order after the clean-baseline step was unavailable. I am not changing optimizer yet because LR remains the highest-value unresolved variable inside the current gated recipe.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.2e-3"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 31 starts the gated LR sweep because the clean-baseline rerun was policy-rejected; first callback is downward to LR=1.2e-3 with all other recipe fields fixed.","Judge the run by trajectory shape as well as terminal FVU: smoother monotone descent with equal/better finish supports gated at lower LR; uniformly slower/worse suggests 1.6e-3 was already near-correct."],"next_hypotheses":["If `gated` at LR=1.2e-3 is smoother and at least as good, try one upward/downward bracket endpoint next to localize the LR optimum.","If `gated` at LR=1.2e-3 is clearly worse across the curve, keep `1.6e-3` as the gated anchor and consider optimizer swap next."],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0003.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 2 的 6e-4 明显劣于 8e-4，说明当前 topk/signum 主线更像是欠步长而不是过冲；本轮只把学习率上调到 1e-3，检验更积极的步长是否能在相同 family/optimizer/K 下带来更快且仍稳定的收敛，并刷新 K=128 的 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕 topk 主线推进，不开新 family，不换优化器，不动 K。本轮唯一主变量仍是 LR：从参考配方 8e-4 上调到 1e-3，回答“signum+topk 在当前设置下是否更需要稍大的学习率”这个单一问题。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮保持单变量且遵循主线顺序，先把 LR 维度补全到高于 baseline 的一侧，再决定是否切 optimizer。风险是 1e-3 可能带来震荡，但这正是本轮要验证的核心问题；若曲线恶化，后续就有充分理由结束 signum 的 LR 扫描并转向 optimizer 对比。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 3 继续只调 LR，补完 signum 在 baseline 以上一侧的步长测试。","r2 的 6e-4 比 baseline 更差，初步说明问题不像是 LR 过大，更可能是步长偏小导致收敛不足。","本轮重点看曲线是否出现更快下降且仍稳定；若 1e-3 出现明显震荡或最终更差，就可结束 signum 的主线 LR 扫描并转向 optimizer 比较。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 1e-3 优于 8e-4，下一轮继续只调 LR，在 8e-4 到 1e-3 之间或略高处做细化。","如果 1e-3 与 8e-4 接近但更不稳，下一轮可结束 signum 的 LR 扫描，按顺序只改 optimizer。","如果 1e-3 明显更差且有震荡，说明 signum 的合适 LR 区间已基本摸清，下一轮应切到 optimizer 维度。"],"primary_variable":"lr"}
