research/history/round_summaries/round_0173.json:25:    "self_review": "This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` and explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe. After `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` underperformed and `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` hit repeated policy-detection issues, the highest-value remaining matched probe is `lowrank_grouped_soft_codebook_residual`: it keeps the same compatible formula class, should stay budget-feasible at EF=2, and tests whether the coarse codebook branch still carries value when residual selection is simplified by local competition.",
