research/history/round_summaries/round_0167.json:78:    "description": "Run one valid matched architecture probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` with the mainline `K=128`, `EF=2`, `signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` recipe explicitly pinned. This cleanly answers whether asymmetric stage allocation is worth any further attention in the current LUTurbo-compatible low-EF regime.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0167.json:79:    "self_review": "This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` while explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe fields that previously caused policy rejection. It is the highest-value remaining matched probe because the other feasible low-EF compatible families already have actual EF=2 results, whereas this asymmetric variant has not yet received a valid run. Risk: historical high-EF evidence for asymmetric staging was weak, so this may simply confirm that fixed front-loading is not worth continuing.",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0147.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_signal","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r145 表明把 signum 学习率从主线参考值 3.0e-3 小幅上调到 3.3e-3 后，FVU 从 0.058106 降到 0.057939，且总耗时未恶化；r146 的 policy_reject 说明不能把这一步包装成 clean baseline，本轮必须继续作为单变量 LR 问题处理。本轮只回答一个问题：相对于当前主线参考配方的 LR=3.0e-3，把 LR 改为 3.3e-3 的收益是否可重复成立，并且不会以更差的 tokens_per_sec、总耗时或 final_total_tokens 为代价。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 LR=3.3e-3 再次优于 3.0e-3，且运行代价基本不变，则可把 3.3e-3 视为新的 signum 主线锚点，后续再决定是否继续微调或转入 optimizer/成本轴。","若 LR=3.3e-3 回落到 3.0e-3 基线附近，则说明 r145 更可能是噪声收益，后续应关闭上探并保守回到 3.0e-3。","若 LR=3.3e-3 只带来极小收益但显著拖慢训练，则将其视为负面 recipe 信号，不再继续围绕更高 LR 上探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r145 首次在 EF=2/K=128/signum 主线上得到 0.057939，因此当前最有价值的问题是确认这个 LR 信号是否可复现。","r146 的 policy_reject 表明必须把 3.3e-3 继续视为 LR 轴单变量问题，而不是以 clean baseline 名义提交。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 与导出形式全部固定，不混入成本轴、loss 轴或新的结构变化。这样既符合当前推荐顺序，也避开了 r146 暴露出的 clean-baseline 包装问题。风险是再次运行 3.3e-3 可能只复现到接近 3.0e-3 的结果，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕当前主线 family 推进，不开新 family；将 r145 的 3.3e-3 结果当作单变量 LR 信号而非新 baseline，保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 不变，再运行一次 LR=3.3e-3，确认该小幅上调是否能稳定优于参考配方的 3.0e-3。","touched_files":[]}
