research/history/logs/agent_action_0106.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Rounds 104 and 105 established a clean, repeatable `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` K128 baseline at `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=2.0e-3`, so the next single mainline question is the first within-family learning-rate probe. Lowering `LR` to `1.6e-3` tests whether this two-stage soft-codebook recipe is slightly underdamped and could trade a bit of early speed for better late-stage descent and a lower terminal FVU; the decision should come from the whole curve shape versus the archived baseline, not just the last point.","summary":"Stay on the `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline and change only `LR` from `2.0e-3` to `1.6e-3`, while keeping `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and `OPTIMIZER=signum` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This follows the required sequence after confirming the new baseline: stay on the same family, keep `K` and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and change exactly one primary variable, `lr`. The main risk is that `1.6e-3` may simply slow a recipe already well tuned at `2.0e-3`, but this is the cleanest first LR-localization question before considering an upward probe or opening the optimizer branch.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 106 is the first LR probe for the confirmed `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline baseline at `K=128`, `EF=12`, and `signum`.","Judge this run by the full trajectory against the archived `LR=2.0e-3` baseline, especially whether the lower step size improves late descent or only slows the whole curve.","If `LR=1.6e-3` regresses or converges too slowly, the next LR probe should return upward rather than continuing downward."],"next_hypotheses":["If `LR=1.6e-3` improves endpoint or late-curve shape versus `2.0e-3`, archive it as the new mainline LR for `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`.","If `LR=1.6e-3` is clearly slower or worse, test only the symmetric upward probe at `LR=2.4e-3` next before opening the optimizer branch.","Do not change optimizer, loss, preprocess, or `K` until the signum LR bracket is localized."],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0162.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，alpha_i 是单样本 top-k 选出的稀疏系数，因此最终表示是单静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.5x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，并显著低于当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x。本轮严格保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主要 recipe 不变，只将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 改为 topk，回答唯一问题：在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下，这条最朴素、最低复杂度的单库稀疏路线是否仍值得继续，还是其表示能力会明显落后于带 trunk、soft-codebook 和 staged refinement 的主线结构。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 topk 明显落后于当前主线，则说明最简单单库稀疏路线在当前 regime 下不值得继续，下一轮回到主线。","若 topk 与当前主线差距小于预期且运行代价更优，则记录其为更简单的低成本备选，但下一轮仍按要求回到主线。","若 topk 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 的系统级收益需要重新审视，但本轮仅做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为直接兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","r159-r161 已依次检验去掉 second stage、去掉 soft-codebook coarse branch、以及更低成本 factorized 单库路线的价值；本轮补充最朴素直接兼容单库 baseline，完成当前低 EF regime 下的主干结构对照。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把质量差异与吞吐波动混淆。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 topk 是因为它是当前尚未在这一严格 matched 配方下补齐的最简单直接兼容基线，能用一次最低复杂度对照回答“主线结构是否真的必要”这个剩余问题。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为 topk，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断这种最简单的直接兼容单库架构是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0133.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"pareto_cost_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 时已满足 selection_cost ≤ 1.5×h×n，本轮不再继续无收益的 LR/loss 试探，而只改一个部署相关主变量：将 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 32，测试是否能在进一步降低 encoder selection_cost 与 trunk/codebook deploy 成本的同时，把 FVU 保持在接近当前 0.0581 的水平，从而形成新的 cost-FVU Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 TRUNK_RANK=32 能明显降成本且 FVU 仅小幅退化，可继续细扫更低或中间 rank 以压出新的 Pareto 前沿。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 明显恶化，则说明当前 trunk 容量已接近下限，后续应回到默认 rank 并改测 NUM_CODES。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 与 baseline 几乎等价且吞吐更好，则可将更低 rank 视为新的 clean baseline，再继续 recipe 搜索。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 继续保证选择成本在硬约束内；本轮通过降低 TRUNK_RANK 探索更低成本 Pareto，而不是追求单点最优 FVU。","r132 表明 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 与 baseline 基本等价，因此暂时结束 loss 轴试探，转向更有系统价值的成本轴。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 均固定，只改 TRUNK_RANK。该动作直接服务于 LUTurbo 的真实目标，因为它同时触碰 encoder 选择成本与部署 trunk 成本；风险是 trunk 容量下降可能导致 coarse branch 表达不足，因此必须结合 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和最终 token 数一起判断是否值得保留。","summary":"在低成本可行主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 上做一次成本轴探索：固定 EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3，仅把 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 32，判断能否以更低 selection/deploy 成本维持接近当前 frontier 的重构质量。","touched_files":[]}
