research/history/round_summaries/round_0063.json:25:    "self_review": "This obeys the Round 63 policy by changing exactly one primary variable: architecture. `bucketed_topk` is a cleaner probe than batch-coupled variants because it stays single-sample and export-compatible, and it is a cleaner runtime-aligned probe than heavier multi-stage or multi-branch families because it only asks whether light selector specialization helps enough to matter at all.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0063.json:52:      "`bucketed_topk` remains directly compatible with LUTurbo export because the final reconstruction is still a finite weighted sum over a static decoder library with fixed `K`; the architecture change is confined to encoder-side bucket specialization before top-k selection.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0063.json:53:      "Judge this probe strictly as a family-worthiness test against matched `gated` K128: if it is clearly worse, discard it and return to the `gated` mainline next round; if it is competitive, record the result but still return to the mainline per policy."
research/history/round_summaries/round_0063.json:56:      "If `bucketed_topk` is clearly worse than matched `gated`, discard the family and return to the `gated` mainline next round.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0063.json:78:    "self_review": "This obeys the Round 63 policy by changing exactly one primary variable: architecture. `bucketed_topk` is a cleaner probe than batch-coupled variants because it stays single-sample and export-compatible, and it is a cleaner runtime-aligned probe than heavier multi-stage or multi-branch families because it only asks whether light selector specialization helps enough to matter at all.",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0203.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"matched_probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j，其中仅将两阶段 residual refinement 的预算分配改为前重后轻，近似 stage1_k≈0.75K、stage2_k≈0.25K。low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，soft codebook 项 Σ_m pi_m c_m 可导出为静态 codebook 库上的加权和，两阶段 residual 项仍可导出为静态 residual 字典上的有限稀疏加权和，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路。兼容性判断为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，固定前置更多 stage1 预算是否能比对称 two-stage 更好地利用有限 K，从而判断 asymmetric two-stage 这条 family 在低 EF 可部署 regime 下是否值得继续。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若该 asymmetric probe 明显劣于对称主线或运行更慢，则关闭该 family，下一轮按策略回到 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线。","若该 probe 的 FVU 接近或优于主线且吞吐不差，则记录 asymmetric budget split 为值得保留的结构变体，但下一轮仍回到主线。","若运行代价上升而收益很小，则把固定前置 stage budget 视为负面信号，不继续在该 family 上展开 STAGE1_RATIO 搜索。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的导出路径与当前主线同类，仍是 trunk 静态库 + codebook 静态库 + 两阶段 residual 静态字典的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","该 family 在 EF=2 下与当前 two-stage 主线处于同一选择成本量级并满足 1.5x encoder selection-cost 硬约束，因此适合作为最后一个高价值 matched architecture probe。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更慢训练误判成结构收益。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这次沿用 r202 已验证通过的 architecture action 形状：architecture 只由 family_name 指定，不在 env_overrides 中重复声明。相比继续重复已得到有效结果的 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 或 lowrank_residual，这个 asymmetric two-stage 变体是当前最有信息价值且尚未获得有效 matched 运行的可行 family。","summary":"执行一个合法的 matched architecture probe：family_name 切到 lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该 family 的最终重构仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态查表链路，兼容性为扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即固定前置更多 stage1 稀疏预算的 asymmetric two-stage 结构在当前低 EF regime 下是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0144.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_baseline","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。经过 r141-r143 的 matched architecture probes 后，当前已经重新确认 two-stage soft-codebook 主线在质量上显著优于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual、lowrank_residual 与 factorized_topk，但这些 probe 的总耗时更短，说明近期运行代价结论可能混杂了架构差异而非主线 recipe 漂移。本轮只回答一个问题：回到主线参考配方 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 做一次 clean baseline 复验，当前 feasible 主线的 FVU、训练曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens 是否仍稳定可复现，从而为后续继续做主线 recipe 调整提供干净锚点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 继续稳定复现 0.0581 附近且运行代价正常，则下一轮继续留在主线 family，优先做一个单变量 recipe 问题而不是继续开 architecture probe。","若 clean baseline 的吞吐或总耗时明显恶化而 FVU 不变，则优先把这视为运行时信号，而不是误判为主线架构退化。","若 clean baseline 本身出现曲线漂移或终点退化，则先重新建立主线锚点，再决定是否进入 LR 或成本轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r141-r143 三个 matched architecture probes 已把更简化候选的质量下界看清：单阶段 soft-codebook、plain lowrank residual、factorized_topk 都未超过当前主线。","在 probe 轮次后先补 clean baseline，有助于分离架构差异与近期运行代价波动，避免后续 recipe 归因失真。"],"primary_variable":"clean_baseline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：本轮不新开 family，不改 K、EF、optimizer、LR，也不混入额外成本轴或 loss 轴变量，只做主线 clean baseline 复验。该动作符合当前推荐顺序：EF 已确认在预算内，且经过连续架构探针后，先恢复可信主线锚点比直接继续调 recipe 更稳。风险是这一轮可能再次得到与现有主线相同的 FVU，但它能提供必要的运行代价参照，避免把架构探针的更短时长误读为主线 recipe 问题。","summary":"回到当前主线参考配方做一次 clean baseline 复验：固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3，不引入任何新结构或新 recipe，只确认当前 feasible 主线的 FVU、训练曲线与运行代价是否仍稳定可复现。","touched_files":[]}
