research/history/logs/agent_action_0044.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 43 was not a marginal win: enabling Hadamard on the strengthened `gated` anchor improved the full curve from start through end and lowered `K=128` FVU from `0.148156` to `0.142923`, while still improving late. Before treating preprocess as the new operative mainline and moving on to K, the next single question should be a clean confirmation run of the exact Hadamard recipe: does this gain reproduce under the current stack, or was Round 43 an unusually favorable draw?","summary":"Run a clean control on the updated `gated` preprocess recipe. Keep `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and the same runtime knobs fixed, and explicitly keep `USE_HADAMARD=1` to verify that the large Round 43 improvement is reproducible. Judge this run by the full trajectory, not just terminal FVU: if the start, mid, and late curve again sit materially below the plain-input anchor and finish near `0.142923`, promote Hadamard as the true `gated` reference recipe; if it falls back toward the non-Hadamard curve, treat the improvement as less stable and avoid overcommitting before K mapping.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the same family, respects the fixed `EF=12` rule, and keeps the work on the current preprocess branch rather than opening a new axis prematurely. I am not moving to K yet because the Round 43 gain was large enough that it deserves one direct confirmation before being treated as the new mainline recipe. The main risk is spending a round without frontier improvement, but the value is higher-confidence attribution of the biggest recent recipe gain.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"1"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 43 produced a substantial full-curve improvement for `gated@128` by enabling Hadamard at `LR=2.0e-3`, lowering FVU to `0.142923` with better early, mid, and late values than the plain-input anchor.","Round 44 is a clean confirmation rerun of the exact Hadamard recipe so the preprocess gain can be classified as a stable new anchor or a one-off before continuing to K exploration."],"next_hypotheses":["If the Hadamard recipe reproduces near the Round 43 curve and endpoint, adopt it as the new `gated` mainline reference and then resume K mapping from `K=96` or `K=64` downward under the improved recipe.","If the rerun materially degrades toward the plain-input baseline, keep the preprocess result provisional and avoid broad K conclusions until recipe stability is clearer."],"primary_variable":"preprocess"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0159.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.75x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，并且比当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x 更低。当前 round 159 只允许一个 matched architecture probe，因此保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 以及主要 recipe 完全不变，仅将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成其最邻近的单阶段父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，回答唯一问题：在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下，第二阶段 residual refinement 是否仍然值得保留，还是单阶段 soft-codebook 版本已经提供了更优的系统级 cost-FVU 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 明显落后于 two-stage 主线，则说明第二阶段 refinement 在当前低 EF regime 下仍然有价值，下一轮回到主线继续 recipe 轴。","若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 与 two-stage 接近且成本更低，则记录其为更强的低成本备选 family，但下一轮仍按要求回到当前主线。","若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 本身值得重新审视，但本轮只做架构价值判断，不立即连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为扩展兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更低 FVU 或更低成本误判为吞吐波动导致的假信号。","该 probe 的核心问题不是刷新 frontier，而是判断 two-stage 结构增量在当前可部署低 EF regime 下是否仍然值得继续。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 而不是更远的 topk 或 factorized_topk，是因为它是当前主线的最近父节点，能最干净地隔离“第二阶段 residual refinement 本身是否值得”这个问题，同时还能给出更低 selection_cost 的直接对照。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为其单阶段父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断第二阶段 refinement 在当前低成本 regime 下是否仍然值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
