research/history/logs/agent_action_0111.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"After five consecutive non-improving mainline rounds, the single highest-value matched architecture probe is the nearest strong alternative family `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`. It preserves the same LUTurbo-compatible static export form as the current `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline, but changes only the stage allocation structure. Holding `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=2.0e-3` fixed isolates one clean question: does the asymmetric two-stage variant remain competitive enough on the matched reference recipe to deserve future follow-up, or should focus stay on the simpler current mainline family.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If the matched `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` probe is clearly worse than the current mainline, return next round to `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` recipe work and do not extend this branch.","If the matched probe is competitive on full-curve shape or endpoint, record it as a viable reserve family but still return next round to the `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline.","Do not change `K`, optimizer, loss, or preprocess in this probe; this round is only about whether the architecture itself is worth keeping in consideration."],"notes_to_memory":["Round 111 uses the one allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` against the current `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline reference recipe.","Judge this probe by the whole curve versus the archived symmetric mainline at `K=128`, `EF=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, not only the terminal FVU.","Regardless of outcome, next round should return to the `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline rather than opening another new family immediately."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This follows the Round 111 probe policy exactly: one matched architecture probe, same `K`, same optimizer, same LR, explicit `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and only `ARCHITECTURE` changes. The chosen family is the strongest nearby LUTurbo-compatible alternative already seen in history, so it gives the highest information value without opening a broader search branch. The tradeoff is spending one round away from mainline recipe cleanup, but that is explicitly allowed for this single probe.","summary":"Use the one allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`, keeping `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=2.0e-3` fixed and changing only `ARCHITECTURE`.","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0121.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.4e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j，可导出为 trunk 库 U、soft-codebook 库 {c_m} 与 residual 字典库 {b_i} 上的有限加权和，因此属于扩展兼容。基于当前可行主线点 K=128, EF=2, signum, LR=3.0e-3 已经满足 selection_cost≈1.25x 的预算约束，本轮只下调学习率到 2.4e-3，测试是否能在不改变 selection/deploy 成本的前提下减少高 K 配方的优化噪声并把 FVU 从 0.0581 继续压低。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 2.4e-3 曲线更平滑但收敛偏慢，回测 2.7e-3 作为同 family 的中间 LR。","若 signum 在 EF=2, K=128 下已明显平台化，再做 optimizer 轴切换并联动 LR retune。","若 K=128 的收益相对 K=96 不足以覆盖更高 deploy 成本，则回到 K 轴比较 96 vs 128 的系统性价比。"],"notes_to_memory":["本 family 维持扩展兼容：x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j，可静态导出到多个向量库。","本轮严格保持 family/K/EF/optimizer 不变，只测 LR，对 frontier 归因干净。","目标是验证可行预算区间内 K=128, EF=2 的主线点是否仍有纯优化改进空间。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守了单变量原则，并继续沿当前主线 family 推进。缺点是我没有直接看到最新训练曲线，只能依据现有结果做保守 LR 下调；但这仍是当前优先级下最可解释、最低风险的一步。","summary":"在预算内主线 family 上做一次纯 LR 清洗：固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、K=128、EF=2、signum，仅把 LR 从 3.0e-3 下调到 2.4e-3，验证是否能以相同 selection_cost/deploy_cost 换取更低 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0191.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk U(Vx)、soft codebook 库 {c_m} 与 residual 字典 {b_i} 都可静态导出到 LUTurbo 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’链路，因此该 family 属于扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，去掉第二阶段 residual refinement 后，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 仍可能以更低的 encoder 选择成本与更快训练吞吐保住一个有价值的 Pareto 点；若 FVU 明显回退，则说明 stage-2 是当前主线真正有效的结构增益。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若该 probe 的 FVU 仍显著落后于 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK / NUM_CODES / STAGE1_RATIO。","若该 probe 以更低 selection_cost 保持接近 FVU 且训练更快，可把 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 重新视为低成本支线继续做单轴 recipe 清洗。","继续避免 routed / bucketed matched probe at EF=2，因为其 selection_cost 约 2.25x h×n，已超 policy 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外显式保持 K=128、EF=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 为扩展兼容，导出路径是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","在 EF=2 下，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 的 selection_cost 约 0.75x h×n，低于主线 two-stage 的 1.25x；routed / bucketed 同配方约 2.25x，当前不可行。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这不是全新 family，信息增益低于真正新结构；但在当前 matched、兼容、且满足成本约束的候选里，它是最干净的 probe。最近的 grouped/gated/asymmetric siblings 已给出负信号，而 routed/bucketed 在 EF=2 被预算拦截，因此本轮用 one-stage parent 来隔离‘第二阶段 residual 是否值得其额外成本’是最可解释的动作。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：把主线从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 切到其 one-stage 父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128 / EF=2 / signum / LR=3.0e-3 不变。该 family 的 LUTurbo 导出公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，属扩展兼容；本轮重点看去掉 stage-2 后，是否能用更低 encoder 选择成本与更快训练代价维持一个值得保留的 Pareto 点。","touched_files":[]}
