research/history/round_summaries/round_0004.json:106:    "description": "\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5 topk \u4e3b\u7ebf\u63a8\u8fdb\uff0c\u4e0d\u5f00\u65b0 family\uff0c\u4e0d\u6362\u4f18\u5316\u5668\uff0c\u4e0d\u52a8 K\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf\u662f\u5b66\u4e60\u7387\uff1a\u4ece 1e-3 \u5c0f\u5e45\u4e0a\u8c03\u5230 1.2e-3\uff0c\u56de\u7b54\u201csignum+topk \u7684\u66f4\u4f18 LR \u662f\u5426\u5728 1e-3 \u4e4b\u4e0a\u201d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5355\u4e00\u95ee\u9898\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0127.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"matched_probe","hypothesis":"本轮 matched architecture probe 只改 architecture。候选架构的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。与当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 相比，它只去掉第二阶段 residual refinement，保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。这个 probe 只回答一个问题：两阶段 residual refinement 在低 EF 可行预算区间内是否真的值得，还是单阶段 soft-codebook residual 已能以更低 selection_cost 给出更好的系统权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 matched probe 明显差于两阶段主线，则说明第二阶段 residual 在低 EF=2 下仍然有价值，下一轮回到主线继续做 recipe/成本轴微调。","若 matched probe 接近或优于当前主线，同时训练更快或 selection_cost 更低，则可考虑把 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 纳入兼容 frontier。","若 matched probe FVU 略差但时间和成本明显更优，则后续可在该 family 内只做主线级别的小步 recipe 清洗，而不是立即扩大家族搜索。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是单次 matched architecture probe，严格保持 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变，只改变 architecture。","选择 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 作为 probe，是为了直接测试‘第二阶段 residual 是否值得’这一最小结构差异问题。","该 probe family 为扩展兼容，可导出路径为 trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + residual 字典库。","评估时需同时比较 FVU、selection_cost、总耗时、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens，避免只按最终 FVU 做结论。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"遵守了本轮 matched architecture probe 规则，只改 architecture，且选择了与主线最接近、兼容且预算内的父节点做对照。风险是 deploy 成本差异可能不大，但它能最干净地回答两阶段 refinement 本身�soft-codebook variants because their EF=2 encoder selection cost is already over budget (~2.5x original matmul) and would be policy-blocked.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe with ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual while keeping K=128, EF=2, signum, and LR=3.0e-3 fixed. It is LUTurbo 扩展兼容 with reconstruction x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j, and it is the nearest feasible architecture variant to the current mainline without adding extra encoder-cost/routing overhead.","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0067.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Rounds 65 and 66 established a clean, reproducible `two_stage_residual` mainline baseline at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, so the next highest-value single question is whether a modest learning-rate reduction improves late-stage convergence without giving up the strong early progress. This round tests only that: does lowering `LR` from `2.0e-3` to `1.6e-3` produce a smoother or better `two_stage_residual` training curve under the same matched recipe.","summary":"Run a single learning-rate adjustment within the `two_stage_residual` mainline by keeping `ARCHITECTURE=two_stage_residual`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and `OPTIMIZER=signum` fixed, and changing only `LR` from `2.0e-3` to `1.6e-3`.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"mainline_improvement","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This follows the prescribed mainline order: the clean baseline has been confirmed, so the next step is a single LR test before touching optimizer, loss, or K. A modest LR reduction is the most interpretable first move because it probes whether the staged residual architecture is currently slightly underdamped near convergence rather than underpowered.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 67 is the first mainline recipe adjustment for `two_stage_residual` after the clean baseline repeat reproduced the Round 65 result.","Judge this run by curve shape as well as endpoint: the question is whether a slightly lower LR improves stability or late-stage descent relative to the archived `2.0e-3` baseline.","If `1.6e-3` is worse or simply slower everywhere, the next LR move should likely be upward rather than making more small downward steps."],"next_hypotheses":["If `LR=1.6e-3` improves the endpoint or gives a cleaner descending curve, archive it as the new `two_stage_residual` mainline recipe.","If `LR=1.6e-3` is clearly worse or just slower than `2.0e-3`, revert to the archived baseline and test a modest LR increase next.","If the curve shape is mixed, keep optimizer fixed and use one more LR probe before considering any optimizer change."],"primary_variable":"learning_rate"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0132.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。由于 r131 的 optimizer 分支被 policy_reject，先停止继续扫 optimizer；本轮只回答一个问题：在主线 baseline（signum, LR=3.0e-3）上去掉 auxiliary K loss（AUXK_ALPHA=0.0）后，是否能改善训练末段收敛形状并在不增加选择成本、不过度拖慢 tokens_per_sec/总耗时的前提下降低 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 曲线更平滑且终点更好，可继续围绕 aux loss 强度做单变量细扫。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 终点变差或训练早期明显失稳，则说明 auxiliary 信号仍有价值，回到 baseline 后再考虑 preprocess 轴。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 与 baseline 几乎等价，则结束 loss 轴试探，后续再评估更细的部署成本变量如 TRUNK_RANK 或 NUM_CODES。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容；本轮不引入新 family。","EF=2 继续满足 selection_cost 预算；K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与 loss 轴混杂。","r131 optimizer 分支被 policy_reject，因此本轮转向更保守的 loss 轴单变量试探，而不是继续扩张 optimizer 搜索。"],"primary_variable":"auxk_alpha","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、主优化器和 LR 都固定，只改 AUXK_ALPHA。该提案避开了刚被 policy 拒绝的 optimizer 分支，继续在兼容且成本可行的主线 family 上获取可解释信号；风险是 auxiliary loss 关闭后可能导致早期 support 学习变差，因此必须结合曲线形状与运行代价共同判断。","summary":"在已稳定复现的 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线上做一次 loss 轴最小改动：固定 EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3，仅关闭 auxiliary K loss，判断该辅助项是否在当前低 EF 可行区间内已经成为收敛噪声。","touched_files":[]}
