research/history/round_summaries/round_0110.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 110 should answer exactly one mainline recipe question on `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`: whether optimizer choice helps on the controller-declared reference recipe. The family already has a clean baseline at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and although `LR=2.4e-3` looked promising, the last round was policy-rejected because optimizer and LR were effectively coupled. Holding the official reference recipe fixed and changing only `OPTIMIZER` to `adam` is the cleanest compliant test of whether this family has optimizer headroom before any optimizer-local LR callback.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0110.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0110.json:24:    "family_stage": "mainline",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0110.json:25:    "self_review": "This stays on the required family, keeps `K=128` and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and changes only one primary axis: optimizer. It matches the round policy order and avoids repeating Round 109's mixed optimizer-plus-LR error. The tradeoff is that it tests `adam` against the official `LR=2.0e-3` anchor rather than the unofficial `2.4e-3` signum setting, but that is the cleaner and safer comparison under the current controller policy.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0110.json:79:    "self_review": "This stays on the required family, keeps `K=128` and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and changes only one primary axis: optimizer. It matches the round policy order and avoids repeating Round 109's mixed optimizer-plus-LR error. The tradeoff is that it tests `adam` against the official `LR=2.0e-3` anchor rather than the unofficial `2.4e-3` signum setting, but that is the cleaner and safer comparison under the current controller policy.",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0001.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"在当前 frontier 为空且主线 family 仍是 topk 的情况下，先跑一轮显式锁定的 clean baseline，能先验证训练链路稳定、拿到可解释的曲线形状与基准 FVU，再决定后续优先做 lr 微调还是优化器切换。","summary":"执行主线 topk 参考配方的 clean baseline，不开新 family，不改代码，不先动 K。用完整 env_overrides 显式锁定 ARCHITECTURE=topk、K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=12、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=8e-4 及其余关键运行参数，优先消除变量隔离失效风险，并建立 round 1 的可比较基线。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮不是为了直接拿更低 FVU，而是为了建立干净基线。风险是收益偏信息获取而非性能提升，但这符合当前“frontier 为空先补 clean baseline”的主线策略，也避免在没有曲线参考时过早调 lr 或换优化器。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"8e-4"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 1 先建立 topk clean baseline，避免 frontier 为空时直接做 lr/optimizer 归因不清。","本轮显式锁定 EF=12 与主线参考 recipe，重点观察整段训练曲线形状而不只看最终 FVU。","当前仓库无已记录 frontier，且执行层默认值与主线参考配方一致，适合先做一次变量完全隔离的基线运行。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 baseline 曲线平稳但后段仍明显下降未收敛，下一轮优先围绕 topk 只调 LR。","如果 baseline 曲线早早平台化或震荡明显，可尝试只改 LR 做更稳的学习率回调。","只有在 baseline 与一轮 LR 调整后，才考虑切换 optimizer 做同 family 主线比较。"],"primary_variable":"other_param"}
