research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:25:    "self_review": "This stays on the same family, respects the fixed `EF=12` rule, and keeps the work on the current preprocess branch rather than opening a new axis prematurely. I am not moving to K yet because the Round 43 gain was large enough that it deserves one direct confirmation before being treated as the new mainline recipe. The main risk is spending a round without frontier improvement, but the value is higher-confidence attribution of the biggest recent recipe gain.",
