research/history/round_summaries/round_0118.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0118.json:8:  "family_stage": "mainline",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0118.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002low-rank trunk\u3001soft codebook\u3001\u4e24\u9636\u6bb5 residual \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u8be5 family \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u5f53\u524d EF=2 \u5df2\u7a33\u5b9a\u6ee1\u8db3 encoder \u9009\u62e9\u6210\u672c\u786c\u7ea6\u675f\uff0c`signum + LR=3.0e-3` \u662f\u5df2\u590d\u73b0\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u4e3b\u7ebf\u951a\u70b9\uff0c\u800c `adam` \u5728\u540c\u914d\u65b9\u4e0b\u76f4\u63a5\u7206\u70b8\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e optimizer \u5206\u652f\u53ef\u6682\u65f6\u5173\u95ed\u3002\u6309\u4e3b\u7ebf\u987a\u5e8f\uff0c\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u5e94\u8fdb\u5165 loss/preprocess \u8f74\uff1b\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf `AUXK_ALPHA`\uff0c\u5c06\u5176\u4ece\u9ed8\u8ba4 `0.03125` \u4e0b\u8c03\u5230 `0.015625`\uff0c\u56de\u7b54\u552f\u4e00\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u4f4e EF \u53ef\u90e8\u7f72 regime \u4e0b\uff0c\u8f83\u5f31\u7684\u8f85\u52a9\u7a00\u758f\u6b63\u5219\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u51cf\u5c11\u5bf9\u4e3b\u91cd\u6784\u76ee\u6807\u7684\u5e72\u6270\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u6539\u5584 FVU\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u51e0\u4e4e\u4e0d\u589e\u52a0\u8bad\u7ec3\u8fd0\u884c\u4ee3\u4ef7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0118.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0118.json:24:    "family_stage": "mainline",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:8:  "family_stage": "mainline",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 时已满足 selection_cost ≤ 1.5×h×n，本轮不再继续无收益的 LR/loss 试探，而只改一个部署相关主变量：将 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 32，测试是否能在进一步降低 encoder selection_cost 与 trunk/codebook deploy 成本的同时，把 FVU 保持在接近当前 0.0581 的水平，从而形成新的 cost-FVU Pareto 点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:24:    "family_stage": "mainline",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:25:    "self_review": "遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 均固定，只改 TRUNK_RANK。该动作直接服务于 LUTurbo 的真实目标，因为它同时触碰 encoder 选择成本与部署 trunk 成本；风险是 trunk 容量下降可能导致 coarse branch 表达不足，因此必须结合 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和最终 token 数一起判断是否值得保留。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:55:      "LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:83:    "self_review": "遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 均固定，只改 TRUNK_RANK。该动作直接服务于 LUTurbo 的真实目标，因为它同时触碰 encoder 选择成本与部署 trunk 成本；风险是 trunk 容量下降可能导致 coarse branch 表达不足，因此必须结合 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和最终 token 数一起判断是否值得保留。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_factorized_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:8:  "family_stage": "mainline",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是 trunk 静态向量库、{b_i} 是 residual 静态向量库；factorized residual scorer 只影响在线选择与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端导出形态，因此可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已证明该 family 在 K=64、EF=1 下能以 0.69x 拿到 0.1256 FVU，当前主矛盾是 trunk 成本过高而不是训练质量不足；本轮严格锚定 r210，只改一个主轴 TRUNK_RANK，从 auto≈256 下调到 32，测试是否能把 total_cost 明确压入 <0.5x 区域，同时尽量保留明显优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:20:    "summary": "相对 r210 的 lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1 做一次严格 param_only 成本压缩，只下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，优先验证能否把该高质量 family 推入 total_cost < 0.5x 区域。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_factorized_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:24:    "family_stage": "mainline",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:55:      "lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出形式稳定为 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态库的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 扩展兼容约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:56:      "r210 的质量信号很强且训练吞吐约 166.6k tokens/s、总耗时 291s，说明该 family 值得优先做成本压缩而不是直接放弃。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:61:      "如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留 r210 作为质量锚点，转向同 family 的单变量 K 轴或回到 topk 前沿继续补点。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:82:    "description": "相对 r210 的 lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1 做一次严格 param_only 成本压缩，只下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，优先验证能否把该高质量 family 推入 total_cost < 0.5x 区域。 [INVALID: launcher did not forward TRUNK_RANK; checkpoint config kept sae.trunk_rank=null, so this result cannot be used to judge TRUNK_RANK=32]",
